{"tid":2202482,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港鐵新動力8.31登報勉港人 管理層急召見 稱有同事「唔開心」","createTime":"2020-09-14T14:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T06:49:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":30,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f52685680a6243758a2039ded101d186a950a6bd","tid":2202482,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T14:59:57.000Z","msg":"港鐵工會「港鐵新動力」早前發起員工眾籌，以工會名義於上月31日《蘋果日報》刊登內頁全版廣告，包括印上「徹查8.31，毋忘7.21」。港鐵新動力今日於工會Facebook透露，他們因登報事件而被港鐵約見，公司指該廣告設計令人誤會，更指有同事對登報內容感到「唔開心」，希望工會尊重、平衡公司及各持份者的立場。港鐵新動力主席陳凱暉回覆時強調，廣告內沒有使用港鐵標誌，並已列明以工會名義刊登，不明白為何仍被誤會，並就部份同事「唔開心」而特意召見他們，坦言：「如果有啲人要戴住有色眼鏡睇，點睇都係有顏色嘅嘢。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200914/3REOSZFS7FHXXKKM3BN3CFXDYQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200914%2F3REOSZFS7FHXXKKM3BN3CFXDYQ%2F&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacStC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=b0f7e827\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200914%2F3REOSZFS7FHXXKKM3BN3CFXDYQ%2F&h=491b3a63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200914/3REOSZFS7FHXXKKM3BN3CFXDYQ/</a>"},{"pid":"f4932a3b2b39e757e9a4dd1e4479cdae51d533a5","tid":2202482,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T15:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"475b2b16ba56d651d3038838358209f907a63e9b","tid":2202482,"uid":61161,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T15:02:22.000Z","msg":"點解唔諗方法令兩邊都開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解係要有一邊唔開心一邊開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ecfaad3771f6633ceb7e5473075da2346114dd","tid":2202482,"uid":267410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14